1
00:00:00,160 --> 00:00:04,720
On the right side of this room are presented writings of foreign authors about Skanderbeg.

2
00:00:05,840 --> 00:00:10,800
Across are writings of national resistance by Albanian authors, end of 19th century.

3
00:00:11,840 --> 00:00:17,040
On the left side are writings by Albanian authors commemorating the 500th anniversary

4
00:00:17,040 --> 00:00:25,520
of Skanderbeg's death, 1968. The Albanian people have inherited generation after generation the

5
00:00:25,520 --> 00:00:32,400
glorious and honorific history led by George Castrioti Skanderbeg. In ceramics, we have songs

6
00:00:32,400 --> 00:00:38,400
and verses by different authors dedicated to Skanderbeg. In the glass cases are exhibited

7
00:00:38,400 --> 00:00:43,520
different objects donated to the museum by individuals in different companies in the world,

8
00:00:43,520 --> 00:00:46,640
but mainly by Albanian that lives abroad.

